data.description: SELLER OFFERING RATE BUY DOWN!! Amazing, move-in ready multi-family residence, with mother-in-law quarters or just more room! This home is perfect! Enter into this light & bright property with inviting entry, featuring contrasting wainscoting, deco tile floor, & vaulted ceilings! Home has so much character & customizations throughout, boasting beautiful tile hardwoods in all living & kitchen, vaulted ceilings with wood beam, brick gas fireplace & chunky mantle beam! Gorgeous white kitchen & breakfast nook is elevated by two-tone island with counter seating, elegant black pantry door, SS appliances, custom lighting, window seat, quartz counters, white subway tile, stunning wallpaper accent wall & grand windows for the perfect amount of natural light! Primary suite includes wall of windows, pretty sconces, dual sink vanity, garden tub for relaxing nights & shower. Secondary bedrms, media & game room are huge! Next Gen space has everything! Walking distance to the community pool & school.
